      "review_summary": "The PR updates Google and OpenRouter image-generation defaults, catalogs, docs, doctor migrations, and tests from retired Gemini preview/Imagen IDs to stable Gemini Flash and Pro image IDs.\n\nPR surface: Source +25, Tests +41, Docs +3. Total +69 across 26 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection shows the PR maps the legacy `nano-banana-pro` doctor migration to Flash while current main maps that same legacy path to a Pro preview model.",
